Prerequisites
=============

Most of the scripts require:

* bash
* Perl (≥ 5.10)
* curl
* jq_ (≥ 1.5)
* cligh_
* git-hub_

.. _jq:
   https://github.com/stedolan/jq

.. _cligh:
   https://github.com/CMB/cligh

.. _git-hub:
   https://github.com/sociomantic-tsunami/git-hub

The ``mail-filter`` script requires:

* Python ≥ 3.2

